<abstract>
<t>This document defines a modification which can be applied to Bellman-Ford (distance vector) algorithm information broadcasting protocols - for example IP RIP, Netware RIP or Netware SAP - which makes it feasible to run them on connection oriented Public Data Networks.</t>
<t>This proposal has a number of efficiency advantages over the Demand RIP proposal (RFC 1582).</t></abstract></front>

